Package gui.Objects

Class GUIObject

java.lang.Object
gui.Objects.GUIObject
Direct Known Subclasses:
GUIButton, GUIInput, GUIRectangle, GUIString, GUITable
public abstract class GUIObject
extends java.lang.Object
This class is the superclass of all other GUIObjects. Properties all GUIObjects need are defined here, such as their position, dimensions and ids.
